description:
It`s the day of the prefectural qualifiers, and Eve and Aoi are a shoo-in to win. That is, if they can keep their arguments from ruining the match!
Source: Crunchyroll

titles.title: Aoi to Eve de Daijoubu? Kaisai, Doubles Senshuken
Are Aoi and Eve Okay Together? The Doubles Championship Begins
葵とイヴで大丈夫? 開催, ダブルス選手権
